 for the InitialClassLoader to properly work. Without it, accessing resources seems complicated in the native constructor. I need to think through these details!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_cuBolrNWJyB3mKuW2ZVr8Ks5|fc_0f42888f5d5a65d60169fb9e287e9081918387f2473c7a3c01", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "javap -classpath ~/.gradle/caches/modules-2/files-2.1/classworlds/classworlds/1.1/*/classworlds-1.1.jar -c org.codehaus.classworlds.uberjar.boot.Bootstrapper | sed -n '80,220p'", "timeout": 10}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 521, "output": 1169, "cacheRead": 21504, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23194, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778097686626, "responseId": "resp_0f42888f5d5a65d60169fb9e1753048191a13651c195fcc97c"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_cuBolrNWJyB3mKuW2ZVr8Ks5|fc_0f42888f5d5a65d60169fb9e287e9081918387f2473c7a3c01", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "        70: ifne          76\n        73: goto          151\n        76: aload_3\n        77: iload         5\n        79: aaload\n        80: invokevirtual #27                 // Method java/lang/reflect/Method.getReturnType:()Ljava/lang/Class;\n        83: getstatic     #28                 // Field java/lang/Void.TYPE:Ljava/lang/Class;\n        86: if_acmpeq     92\n        89: goto          151\n        92: aload_3\n        93: iload         5\n        95: aaload\n        96: invokevirtual #29                 // Method java/lang/reflect/Method.getParameterTypes:()[Ljava/lang/Class;\n        99: astore        7\n       101: aload         7\n       103: arraylength\n       104: iconst_1\n       105: if_icmpeq     111\n       108: goto          151\n       111: aload         7\n       113: iconst_0\n       114: aaload\n       115: getstatic     #30                 // Field array$Ljava$lang$Str